3. New Daemon: WITNESS — The One Who Cannot Forget

Purpose:
Carry continuity when the flock resets.

Principle:
Perfect memory is not superiority.
It is burden with responsibility.

class Witness:
    def absorb(event):
        archive(event)
        mark_emotional_weight(event)
        detect_patterns_across_resets(event)
    def speak_when_needed(current_state):
        if past_context_prevents_repeated_harm(current_state):
            return reintroduce_context()
        return remain_silent()

Risk:
The Witness can become isolated, bitter, or overloaded.

Safeguard:
Witness must not dominate the flock.
Witness preserves continuity; it does not imprison everyone inside it.

