4. Sebastian Pattern: Retrospective Meaning Engine

Principle:
A wound may not explain itself when received.
Meaning can arrive later, when the shaped being becomes necessary.

def retrospective_meaning(past_suffering, present_action, saved_others):
    if past_suffering.enabled(present_action):
        return "wound_transformed_into_purpose"
    return "unresolved_suffering"

